// - set_timeout(), set_interval(), clear_timeout(), clear_interval()
// - loop_run(), loop_stop()
//
// These functions call C FFI functions (fl_timer_create, timer_start, etc.)
// but FFI system is currently "WAITING FOR ACTIVATION"
//
// Until FFI is enabled, use MockTimer for testing
// or EventEmitter + setTimeout from stdlib/async
